Package com.linecorp.armeria.server.jetty

Class JettyServiceBuilder

java.lang.Object
com.linecorp.armeria.server.jetty.JettyServiceBuilder
public final class JettyServiceBuilder
extends Object
Builds a JettyService. Use JettyService.of(Server) if you have a configured Jetty Server instance.
